Name: Swarmlake
About the game: Swarmlake is an ultra-intense first-person shooter ballet about fighting a record-breaking swarm. Powerful : Fight a record-breaking swarm with an overpowered weapon Vertical : Soar through the sky by repeatedly jumping off of enemies Endless : An infinite arena pulsating to the original music Intense : Countless enemies at once thanks to the own game engine Smooth : Deterministic gameplay based on years of feedback Fun : Fast-paced and addictive highscore-chase with online replays
